This is a winner. Great combination of flavors. I add a few drops of good olive oil. I also have used this same combination of ingredients on pizza with great success.

Rating: 4
This is a lovely addition to my crostini/bruschetta repertoire. Very tasty. I do agree that a strong cheese can be overpowering. We used an older imported Italian gorgonzola and it was quite zippy.

